results.title: 4 Engraved Large US Coast Guard Whiskey Stones & Muslin Bag, Perfect Stocking Stuffer, Great US Military Christmas Gift, Made in the USA
results.description:
Whiskey Stones are a Unique and Popular gift on their own, but when they are personalized they become extra special.

This listing is for a set of 4 Large Engraved Whiskey Stones.  They make a great gift for a current or veteran Military hero!  

Christmas, Birthdays, Anniversaries, Military Weddings, Whiskey Stones are always a well received gift.

Each Whiskey Stone measures 1.15" x 1" and is made of 100% Soapstone right here in the USA. Only 1 or 2  are needed per drink.  Each set comes in it's own Muslin Storage bag with an instructions for use card.

The pictured stones are currently engraved with the US Coast Guard Emblem, USCG and the recipients Initials however each order can be customized and I can engrave anything on the Stones, just send me your engraving instructions in the "Notes to Seller" section at check out or send me an Etsy Convo.  If you would like to use a different Military Logo please let me know.

**Please note the listing is for only ONE SIDE of each stone engraved, they can be the same as the main picture or please feel free to switch out any of the images or words and replace them with initials or names etc... Please specify any changes in the Notes to Seller at checkout**

**What are Whiskey Stones?**

Whiskey Stones, are a new way to chill your whiskey or wine without diluting your drink. Ice cubes water down your whiskey and leave a moist layer of condensation on your glass, whiskey stones have all the benefits of ice without the hassles.

Whiskey Stones are made out of cubes of solid soapstone which is softer than granite and won’t scratch your glass. Soapstone retains its temperature much longer than ice, so it will cool your whiskey or liquor of your choice and provide a more sustained chill. Whiskey Stones are also non-porous, odorless and tasteless so they won’t alter your favorite drinks. Whiskey Stones can also be used to warm your drinks and work well with non-alcoholic beverages too.  Whiskey stones are Dishwasher Safe.

Whiskey Stones, are a new way to chill your whiskey or wine without diluting your drink. Ice cubes water down your whiskey and leave a moist layer of condensation on your glass, whiskey stones have all the benefits of ice without the hassles.

Whiskey Stones are made out of cubes of solid soapstone which is softer than granite and won’t scratch your glass. When your order ships, you will receive a convo from us telling you how the package has shipped.

When delivering to residences, it is UPS and the US Mail's policy to not require a signature.  Should you require someone to sign for the package(s) please let us know and we can let you know what the additional cost would be.

The addressee MUST BE KNOWN by the Post Office, UPS, FED-EX or other delivery service to reside at the address you are shipping to.  If the addressee is not known to reside there, you MUST address the label with a C/O (care of) someone that is known to reside there.

If you have us ship to an address, and the Post Office deems it to be UNDERLIVERABLE or UNDELIVERABLE AS ADDRESSED or some similar terminology, and we have addressed the package as you have instructed, our obligation has been completed at that point.  Should the package be returned to us, we will contact you with a new shipping price to re-mail it to you.  Should the package not be returned to us, or returned damage, we will not be responsible for any refund or replacement of any amount.

LOST PACKAGES SHIPPED WITHIN THE UNITED STATES:
If your package does not arrive by the estimated date provided by the post office, UPS or other delivery service, we will decide to either replace or refund your purchase 14 business days, excluding holidays, after the delivery service's estimated delivery date.  The only exception would be FIRST CLASS MAIL, which would be 21 business days, excluding holidays.  This will be an allowable timeframe for misrouted packages to arrive to you.

We have had instances where packages delivered to apartment buildings were delayed as the mailman decided not to leave the package in the hallway unattended.

When we send you the shipping convo, it would be a good idea to arrange to have the package delivered to a neighbor (leave a note for the mailman) or ask the post office to hold any packages at the post office for you to pickup.

UPS WILL LEAVE packages unattended, so you should definately arrange to be home or leave a note for the UPS driver to deliver to a neighbor.  The neighbor would need to be a next door apt as UPS will not deliver to another building free of charge.

CANADIAN and INTERNATIONAL shipments: If you require a tracking number, UPS is the only option. Please contact us to see if the shipping charges shown in the listing is for UPS or Mail. Any duties and taxes will be the responsibility of the customer.  Shipments made to Canada or Internationally by a service other than UPS (ie: Postal Service) are not guarranteed as the tracking numbers are only good until the package reaches the US border, then the receiving country takes control.


INSURANCE:

Any packages delivered to you in a damaged condition MUST be reported to the delivery person BEFORE YOU SIGN for the package.
